nodes.text: Star Tours: "The Ultimate Adventure" is Still the Ultimate Ride at Disneyland

"Star Tours: 'The Ultimate Adventure' is Still the Ultimate Ride at Disneyland" is a feature article in The Lucasfilm Fan Club Magazine 2, written by Lisa E. Cowan. It details the Star Tours ride at Disneyland.
